{"tid":2321117,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黑警偷聽青年對話表示曾向警車掟汽油彈  19歲男生藏雷射筆罪成判入更生中心","createTime":"2020-12-11T09:38:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T19:06:39.000Z","uid":56115,"like":3,"dislike":120,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"c6f593a9f12bce241f43a7a0cfbb1163ff3c9abe","tid":2321117,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T09:38:17.000Z","msg":"19歲男學生過馬路時向同學直認曾向警車掟汽油彈，被身旁的便衣警聽見並截停拘捕，警方其後在未有搜查令下到其住所搜屋，搜出2支雷射筆。男學生早前經審訊後被裁定管有攻擊性武器罪成，王證瑜裁判官今午於屯門裁判法院接納報告建議，判被告入更生中心。<br />\n<br />\n辯方引述被告李德軒的感化官報告指被告合作有禮，犯案因守法意識薄弱，續指其本性不壞，現時已反省並感到後悔。王官指判刑應阻嚇及更生並重，遂接納報告建議，判被告入更生中心。"},{"pid":"8c5f1f0378efe2a7b00cc43cacf7e8c181a3f28b","tid":2321117,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T09:38:42.000Z","msg":"汁: 頭條"},{"pid":"d0e18f5fa068ec7c000dcccb568ecb9036ba1528","tid":2321117,"uid":24345,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T09:39:07.000Z","msg":"silent chicken is important"},{"pid":"2f582d7a0fd9de1cf22a6441788c0568db33263d","tid":2321117,"uid":201604,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T09:39:59.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好亂講野得唔得"},{"pid":"99d04cab452bc80d7db73b535fd64834553148ef","tid":2321117,"uid":51701,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"2f582d7a0fd9de1cf22a6441788c0568db33263d","tid":2321117,"uid":201604,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T09:39:59.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好亂講野得唔得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T09:40:43.000Z","msg":"你覺得真係咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19036bdecee1dc9d34